    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It doesn't feel like a chapter or a transition though. It feels more like... a glitch. Like I'm a ghost haunting my own life. People see the shell and they talk to it, they expect it to respond, but there's just nothing inside anymore. It's exhausting to keep pretending there's still someone home when there's really just this hollow, heavy thing occupying space. It's not sleeping. It's just gone.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
